   <concept id="FAR_19_1309" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">19.1309</ph> 
         Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1272e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>The
contracting officer shall insert the clause <xref href="52.219-3.dita#FAR_52_219_3"
                        base="i1057314"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-3</xref>, Notice of HUBZone
Set-Aside or Sole-Source Award, in solicitations and contracts for
acquisitions that are set aside or awarded on a sole-source basis
to, HUBZone small business concerns under <xref href="19.1305.dita#FAR_19_1305"
                        base="i1099604"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1305</xref> or <xref href="19.1306.dita#FAR_19_1306"
                        base="i1099639"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1306</xref>. This includes
multiple-award contracts when orders may be set aside for HUBZone small
business concerns as described in <xref href="8.405-5.dita#FAR_8_405_5"
                        base="i1117805"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="16.505.dita#FAR_16_505"
                        base="i1104008"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F) or
when orders may be issued directly to one HUBZone small business
concern in accordance with <xref href="19.504.dita#FAR_19_504"
                        base="id203CEK0I0HS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.504</xref>(c)(1)(ii).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1272e34">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-4.dita#FAR_52_219_4"
                        base="i1057352"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-4</xref>, Notice of Price
Evaluation Preference for HUBZone Small Business Concerns, in solicitations
and contracts for acquisitions conducted using full and open competition.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1272e42">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>For use of clause <xref href="52.219-14.dita#FAR_52_219_14"
                        base="id203KG0I04WS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-14</xref>, Limitations
on Subcontracting, see the prescription at <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(e).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1272e53">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> For use
of clause <xref href="52.219-33.dita#FAR_52_219_33"
                        base="id203KG0I04WS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-33</xref>,
Nonmanufacturer Rule, see the prescription at <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="i1100931"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(h).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
